Why Space Exploration is Important to the United States. A version of this essay was first presented at the National Society of Black Engineer's Annual Conference luncheon in Pittsburgh, PA this past April. One of the hardest questions that is often asked of us rocket scientists is why is space exploration important?. Even JFK tried to answer this question many years ago.
